description: Step into refined living at 616 East 4th Street, located in the heart of South Boston. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home resides within a 19th-century brick building, offering a boutique experience with only 24 luxury condominiums. Spanning 1,126 square feet, this home boasts a superb floor plan with oversized windows and high ceilings that prioritizes both comfort and privacy, with the 2 bedrooms strategically positioned to ensure separation from the living area. The modern kitchen is a haven for culinary creativity, with wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, wine chiller and more.  Enjoy modern conveniences with in-unit washer and dryer, central air conditioning, on-demand hot water, custom California Closets, heated two car hydraulic lift garage parking and more, all in an ideal South Boston location with easy access to shops, restaurants, beaches and more.
